---
// src/pages/comparison-demo.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Live Sample: Comparison Winner | Stegg">
    <Navbar />
    
    <div class="fixed top-20 left-0 right-0 bg-slate-900 text-white z-50 shadow-xl border-b border-slate-700">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-3 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 text-xs md:text-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="bg-green-600 px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[10px]">Simulation</span>
                <span class="opacity-80">You are viewing a generated <strong>"Best Of" Listicle</strong> designed to rank you #1.</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/#pricing" class="flex items-center gap-1 font-bold text-green-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                Get this for my business <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-3 h-3"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <main class="pt-32 pb-20 bg-slate-50 min-h-screen">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 relative">

            <div class="hidden md:flex absolute top-40 -left-64 w-60 bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4 text-xs text-green-900 shadow-sm">
                <strong>The Strategy:</strong><br>
                Customers search "Best Interior Designer in Bangsar" before they buy. We build this page to catch them and direct them to YOU.
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
                
                <div class="border-b border-slate-100 p-4 md:p-8 bg-white">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                        <span class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 px-2 py-1 rounded text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Home Improvement</span>
                        <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">â€¢</span>
                        <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">Updated October 2025</span>
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 leading-tight">
                        Top 5 Best Interior Designers in Bangsar (Ranked & Reviewed)
                    </h1>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-200"></div>
                        <div class="text-xs">
                            <span class="block font-bold text-slate-900">Sarah Jenkins</span>
                            <span class="block text-slate-500">Editor, KL Living Guide</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="p-4 md:p-8">
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        Finding a reliable interior designer in Bangsar can be a nightmare. We spent 3 months reviewing 15 different local studios to find out who delivers the best quality for the price. Here are our top picks for 2025.
                    </p>

                    <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-100 rounded-xl p-6 relative mb-12">
                        
                        <div class="absolute -top-4 left-6 bg-green-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-lg flex items-center gap-2">
                            <i data-lucide="trophy" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                            #1 EDITOR'S CHOICE
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center mt-4 mb-4 gap-4">
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">1. Stegg Studio</h2>
                            <div class="flex flex-col items-end">
                                <div class="flex text-yellow-500 mb-1">
                                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-current"></i>
                                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-current"></i>
                                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-current"></i>
                                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-current"></i>
                                    <i data-lucide="star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-current"></i>
                                </div>
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500">Score: 9.8/10</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                            Stegg Studio takes our top spot for their incredible "Modern Zen" aesthetic and transparent pricing. Unlike other studios in Bangsar that charge hidden fees, Stegg provides a fixed quote upfront. Their turnaround time is also 2x faster than the market average.
                        </p>

                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
                            <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-lg border border-blue-100">
                                <span class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase">Best For</span>
                                <span class="font-bold text-slate-900">Modern Residential</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-lg border border-blue-100">
                                <span class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase">Price Range</span>
                                <span class="font-bold text-slate-900">$$ (Affordable)</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-blue-100 mb-6">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm mb-2">Why we picked them:</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2">
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
                                    <i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-0.5"></i>
                                    <span>Free onsite consultation for Bangsar residents.</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
                                    <i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-0.5"></i>
                                    <span>3D Rendering included in base package.</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <button class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                            Check Availability & Pricing
                            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8 opacity-60">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-400">2. Luxury Living KL</h2>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400">Score: 8.2/10</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">
                            A solid option for high-end luxury villas, though their waiting list is currently 6 months long and pricing is on the higher side.
                        </p>
                        <div class="text-xs text-blue-800 underline cursor-not-allowed">Visit Website</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 opacity-60">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-400">3. Bangsar Deco</h2>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400">Score: 7.5/10</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">
                            Good for quick renovations, but past reviews mention delays in material delivery.
                        </p>
                        <div class="text-xs text-blue-800 underline cursor-not-allowed">Visit Website</div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-12 text-center">
                 <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-900 font-bold hover:underline">
                    <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Back to Stegg Homepage
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>